column17:
MTV Black Wrist Watch:
MTV a brand renowned for its modish timepieces presents this trendy watch for those men who love to create their own style statement. The black dial of this watch features a central checkered pattern along with silver coloured markers and hands on it. Elevating the style-quotient of this watch is the MTV brand logo print on the dial. Attached to the lugs of this time gear is a black leather strap with tonal stitches along its edges. Wear this MTV Roadies men watch with a pair of denims and white T-shirt to win a lot of compliments from your peers.
